# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# macOS / iCloud / Finder duplication artefacts.
# When a file gets copied while another process holds it open (iCloud sync,
# Time Machine restore, GitHub Desktop concurrent checkout), Finder names
# the duplicate "<original> 2.<ext>" — these are never wanted in commits.
* 2
* 2.*

